OL,3,C'Remarkable' teacher killed in Air
OL,4,CIndia crash remembered by school
OL,6,FFormer colleagues at Northfleet
OL,7,FNursery School told ITV News
OL,8,FMeridian's Abigail Bracken that Panna
OL,9,FNagar was an inspirational headteacher.
OL,11,FStaff from a nursery school in Kent
OL,12,Fhave been remembering their
OL,13,Finspirational former headteacher who
OL,14,Fwas killed in the Air India crash.
OL,16,FPanna Nagar dedicated much of her life
OL,17,Fto education as a former headteacher
OL,18,Fof Northfleet Nursery School, as an
OL,19,FOfsted inspector, and even funding a
OL,20,Fschool in India.
