OL,3,C'Remarkable' teacher killed in Air
OL,4,CIndia crash remembered by school
OL,6,FThe current headteacher at Northfleet,
OL,7,FNeerasha Singh said: "She was a
OL,8,Fremarkable woman, you know, always
OL,9,Fchampioning education, being key to
OL,10,Fthe success of a child's life. 'If you
OL,11,Fcan dream it, you could have it', was
OL,12,Fher motto.
OL,14,F"She was a true champion, not only for
OL,15,Fearly years within Kent, but across
OL,16,Fthe world."
OL,18,FShe's remembered as a champion for
OL,19,Fboth children and staff.
