OL,3,C'Remarkable' teacher killed in Air
OL,4,CIndia crash remembered by school
OL,6,FNatasha Griggs said: "She's very much
OL,7,Fabout empowering you and making you
OL,8,Fthe best you can be."
OL,10,FAmy Bullen said: "But she also cared
OL,11,Fabout the children, anything she could
OL,12,Fdo for the children, and she would
OL,13,Fhave it implemented within the school.
OL,14,FShe'd always allow us to buy
OL,15,Fresources, everything would be up to
OL,16,Fdate.
OL,18,FRos Munday said: "She never wanted
OL,19,Fpeople to sit on their laurels. It was
OL,20,Fabout right, you can do this, she
OL,21,Fwould support you and nurture you."
