OL,3,C'Remarkable' teacher killed in Air
OL,4,CIndia crash remembered by school
OL,6,FBeverley Price said: "She wanted us to
OL,7,Freach our full potential as well as
OL,8,Fthe children, you know. But she just
OL,9,Finspired everybody around her."
OL,11,FHer death in the Air India plane crash
OL,12,Fearlier this month has been felt by
OL,13,Fthe whole community.
OL,15,FGravesend Hindu Temple has held a
OL,16,Fprayer meeting for all the victims.
OL,18,FThe vice chairman of Om Mandir,
OL,19,FDavinder Sharma, said his daughter
OL,20,Fflourished under Panna Nagar's care.
