OL,6,F"It wasn't just a job for her. She was
OL,7,Fvery, very passionate about what she
OL,8,Fwas doing and that was very much
OL,9,Fevident in her actions and her day to
OL,10,Fday work, what she was doing. So she
OL,11,Fwas very much involved in every
OL,12,Fchildren."
OL,14,FThose who knew her say Panna Nagar
OL,15,Fwill be remembered for helping many
OL,16,Fchildren to dream big around the world.
